The movie_api is the project that defines your endpoints and what the server should send when each enpoint is hit by a request.
Here, our API is connected with our Atlas MongoDB database and the data that are served are served from the Atlas MongoDB database.

This movie_api is hosted on Heroku.
The movie_api is hosted on Heroku in order for users to be able to use our API not only locally, but also remotely through the web.
